Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the deployment process of the ActiveX.NET framework:

```plantuml
@startuml avarghesein_ActiveX.NET

participant "ActiveX.NET.Server" as Server
participant "MEF" as MEF
participant "ActiveXServerContext" as Context
participant "ActiveXServers" as Servers
participant "Plugin DLL" as Plugin
participant "COM Client" as Client

Server -> Server: Start
Server -> Context: Create
Context -> Servers: Initialize
Servers -> MEF: Discover plugins
MEF -> Plugin: Load
Plugin --> MEF: Return IActiveXServer implementations
MEF --> Servers: Return discovered plugins
Servers --> Context: Ready
Context -> Context: Register COM objects
Context -> Context: Start message loop

Client -> Server: COM object request
Server -> Context: Handle request
Context -> Servers: Get IActiveXServer instance
Servers -> Plugin: Create COM object
Plugin --> Servers: Return COM object instance
Servers --> Context: Return COM object
Context --> Client: Return COM object reference

Client -> Server: Release COM object
Server -> Context: Handle release
Context -> Servers: Decrease reference count
Servers -> Plugin: Dispose COM object if count = 0

@enduml
```